N2  - Historiography's potential as a management research technique has not been extensively evaluated. This article describes historiography, evaluates criticism directed toward it, and assesses its usefulness for management research. It asserts that historiography can make significant contributions to variable selection and evaluation, theory building, and hypothesis generation.
